g.text: The above mentioned resource sharing repositories have freely available media archive accounts whose content can
be shared with configured access and edit permissions. Links to their resources can be appended to design strategies
Many allow till 1 Gigs worth of free space which you can freely access to add and delete resources in very easy to use
web interfaces which you can access over the internet. We would recommend Google Drive as an email address with
a Youtube Channel and a Google Site universally compatible with all devices are also available with a web interface.
